Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a bunch of broccoli sealed in plastic wrap in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a bunch of broccoli sealed in plastic wrap in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} or {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
